  <entry>
    <id>https://community.sap.com/t5/technology-q-a/how-to-correct-invalid-time-dependent-md-in-sap-bw/qaq-p/13772803</id>
    <title>How to correct invalid time dependent MD in SAP BW</title>
    <updated>2024-07-26T09:43:41.413000+02:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>GaneshKabra</name>
      <uri>https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/1535459</uri>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;P&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Issue : &lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;UL&gt;&lt;LI&gt;In 0MAT_PLANT incorrect data loaded for Time Dependent master data .&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;/UL&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="GaneshKabra_0-1721979372962.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/142060i49CA1010ED9EAAE0/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="GaneshKabra_0-1721979372962.png" alt="GaneshKabra_0-1721979372962.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Reason :&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;UL&gt;&lt;LI&gt;When loading master data if we select below mentioned checkbox then it will consider as new record and it will create one new wrong entry in Q table&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;/UL&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="GaneshKabra_1-1721979372969.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/142062iEEC7145277D72835/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="GaneshKabra_1-1721979372969.png" alt="GaneshKabra_1-1721979372969.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Resolution :&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;UL&gt;&lt;LI&gt;Execute RSDMD_CHECKPRG_ALL program to correct "From Date" for errored record&amp;nbsp;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;UL&gt;&lt;LI&gt;First execute&amp;nbsp;RSDMD_CHECKPRG_ALL program in check mode so that you will come to know that how many records have issue in data as per below screen shot :&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;/UL&gt;&lt;/UL&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="GaneshKabra_4-1721979498686.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/142064i41829C5B3AE6363B/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="GaneshKabra_4-1721979498686.png" alt="GaneshKabra_4-1721979498686.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;UL&gt;&lt;UL&gt;&lt;LI&gt;Once you get list of Material and Plant which is in error you will get list then execute the same program to repaire the data.&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;So once you executed above program in repaire mode then you will see "from date" is adjusted properly.&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;/UL&gt;&lt;/UL&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="GaneshKabra_2-1721979372972.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/142061iA8BCC9626ED2709E/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="GaneshKabra_2-1721979372972.png" alt="GaneshKabra_2-1721979372972.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;UL&gt;&lt;LI&gt;Then create self loop transformation for 0MAT_PLANT to update releavent attributes.&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;UL&gt;&lt;LI&gt;Write a code in end routine ( ABAP / AMDP ) in newly created transformation in such away that whatever next future records is available we need to set same attributes for errored record. ( This may vary based on business )&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;So in this example i need to show in ZVSSTA_TD = Z1 &amp;amp; ZORDTO_TD = Y for errored record.&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;When i executed self loop DTP for newly created transformation i can able to see below output which we were expecting.&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;/UL&gt;&lt;/UL&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="GaneshKabra_3-1721979372977.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/142063iDFA602920E80E568/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="GaneshKabra_3-1721979372977.png" alt="GaneshKabra_3-1721979372977.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;</content>
    <link href="https://community.sap.com/t5/technology-q-a/how-to-correct-invalid-time-dependent-md-in-sap-bw/qaq-p/13772803"/>
    <published>2024-07-26T09:43:41.413000+02:00</published>
  </entry>
