    </author>
    <content>&lt;P&gt;Hi Experts,&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;We are using a S4HANA and utilising SAP MDG Co-Deployment scenario. We were trying to use Lean App with Request Cost Center and Request Profit Center to create master data in the local system S4HANA 2020. We had configured the workflow using Business rules and process flow is working as expected. However, We are unable to replicate the data across the local S4HANA system where MDG is hosted.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;We were trying to use Standard SAP configuration as below:&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="Tirthankar_Chakraborty1_0-1722352279901.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/144289iB0F7C5AF70B1CBE6/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="Tirthankar_Chakraborty1_0-1722352279901.png" alt="Tirthankar_Chakraborty1_0-1722352279901.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Same is configured against replication model.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="Tirthankar_Chakraborty1_1-1722352604319.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/144291iD4C877777CA4F6B6/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="Tirthankar_Chakraborty1_1-1722352604319.png" alt="Tirthankar_Chakraborty1_1-1722352604319.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;While checking the outbound class, We found that is also triggered as well as proxy is getting generated but data does not get updated.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Since, this was not working, tried to create a operation for inbound as standard SAP didnot give any operation for profit center but that is also not working.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="Tirthankar_Chakraborty1_2-1722352766791.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/144292i1C7FB210D6D1A8B2/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="Tirthankar_Chakraborty1_2-1722352766791.png" alt="Tirthankar_Chakraborty1_2-1722352766791.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;This is the first time i am working on this MDG. Can anyone help on this as how to get it processed via inbound or any pointers. I was trying to check the standard SAP configuration and didnt find any configuration related to the inbound configuration.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Thanks&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Tirthankar&lt;/P&gt;</content>
